tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE trade_execution_records (
  trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  stock_symbol VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE trade_execution_records (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    executed_by VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    security_symbol VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE trade_executions ( 
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
    trade_symbol VARCHAR(50), 
    trade_quantity INT, 
    trade_price DECIMAL(10,2) 
);

CREATE TABLE trade_execution_records (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    execution_date TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT,
    price DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE compliance_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT,
    compliance_date TIMESTAMP,
    rule VARCHAR(100),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE audit_trail (
    audit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    action_date TIMESTAMP,
    user_id INT,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE trades (
  trade_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  trade_date DATE,
  symbol TEXT,
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL,
  executed_by TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE traders (
  trader_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name TEXT,
  last_name TEXT,
  email TEXT,
  phone_number TEXT,
  region TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE counterparties (
  counterparty_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  name TEXT,
  address TEXT,
  city TEXT,
  country TEXT,
  contact_person TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE trade_executions (
  execution_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  trade_id UUID,
  trader_id UUID,
  counterparty_id UUID,
  execution_date TIMESTAMP,
  executed_quantity INT,
  executed_price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE audit_logs (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  action TEXT,
  user_id UUID,
  details JSONB
)
